description: Alien spaceship landed on my car. Not only was I late for my appointment at the dentist, but I found that one of the feet of the spaceship had scratched the duco on my recently restored Mustang. I mean, it's all very well to want to destroy someone else's planet, but scratching someones paintwork is just wrong!
Insect flew into my eye while driving
Tried to drive through cliff wall
Thought I was driving a military tank
Should have stayed at the pub
Should have bought a flying car
Hands got stuck to steering wheel
I wonder if anyone is reading these
Oh it's nearly time to go home
